  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DRC Joint Response</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">World Vision aims to contribute to the following UNOCHA HRP objectives through the DRCJR: 1. Immediate improvement of the lives of people affected by the crisis and in priority the most vulnerable 2. Protecting people affected by the humanitarian crisis and protection of their human rights 3. Reduction of overmortality and overmorbidity of people affected by the crisis</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">World Vision will work in three sectors under the DRCJR: WASH, Protection and Multi-Purpose Cash (to cover non-food needs).</narrative>
  </description>
